T02TD1981E:159a-1: badzra bhee ra wa s'a dha na /
T02TD1981E:159a-3: rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi sgrub thabs /
T02TD1981E:159a-4: dpal rdo rje 'jigs byed ma he'i gdong pa can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1981E:159a-5: bcom ldan 'jig pa'i dus kyi me ltar 'bar //
T02TD1981E:159a-6: drag po'i drag po de la phyag 'tshal nas //
T02TD1981E:159a-7: las rnams thams cad rab sgrub phyir //
T02TD1981E:159a-8: ma he dgong can sgrub thabs cung zhig bri //
T02TD1981E:159a-9: yid dang mthun zhing dben pa'i gnas dag tu //
T02TD1981E:159a-10: ngang gis bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
T02TD1981E:159a-11: ma he'i gdong can skad cig rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1981E:159a-12: lha dang bla ma mnyes byas de 'og tu //
T02TD1981E:159a-13: stong pa ma yin mi stong pa yang min //
T02TD1981E:159a-14: sems nyid spros dang bral ba rnam par bsgom //
T02TD1981E:159a-15: yam las rlung dkyil ram las bskal me 'bar //
T02TD1981E:159a-16: de las h'um 'phros rdo rje'i rang bzhin no //
T02TD1981E:159a-17: aa las zla ba rgyas pa'i steng nyid du //
T02TD1981E:159a-18: dh'i: las 'jam dpal gzhon nu bskyed par bya //
T02TD1981E:159a-19: de yi thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bsam //
T02TD1981E:159a-20: de steng h'um yig nag po 'bar ba blta //
T02TD1981E:159a-21: de nas thams cad yongs gyur rdo rje ste //
T02TD1981E:159a-22: de yongs gyur las bcom ldan ma he'i zhal //
T02TD1981E:159a-23: dbyar gyi char sprin nag po lta bu'i mdog / sku las me 'bar khams gsum skrag par byed //
T02TD1981E:159a-24: khros pas dur khrod thod pa'i do shal byas //
T02TD1981E:159a-25: zhal gcig ma he nag po rgod pa'i zhal //
T02TD1981E:159b-0: rva brag gzhon nu'i zhal gyis @159b rnam par mdzes //
T02TD1981E:159b-1: phyag g-yas rdo rje gdengs sam gri gug 'dzin //
T02TD1981E:159b-2: phyag g-yon thod pa khrag gis bkang ba'o //
T02TD1981E:159b-3: zhabs gnyis gyad kyi dor stabs ro yi steng //
T02TD1981E:159b-4: ma he nag po'i steng du rnam par bsam //
T02TD1981E:159b-5: mngon sum 'dra bar rnam par gsal ba dang //
T02TD1981E:159b-6: snying gar nyi ma 'bar te h'um yig go //
T02TD1981E:159b-7: de las ye shes dgug gzhug dbang bskur bya //
T02TD1981E:159b-8: de nas de nyid skar ma'i tshogs 'dras bskor //
T02TD1981E:159b-9: yengs pa med par rtag tu bzlas pa bya /
T02TD1981E:159b-10: aom hr'im: shri: wi kri kra t'a na na h'um phat /
T02TD1981E:159b-11: 'di ni sngags kyi rgyal po ste //
T02TD1981E:159b-13: 'bum phrag gsum du bzlas pa bya ;
T02TD1981E:159b-14: / de yis las rnams thams cad 'grub //
T02TD1981E:159b-15: gal te ldang bar 'dod pa na //
T02TD1981E:159b-16: ye shes ma he'i zhal la ni //
T02TD1981E:159b-17: mchod cing bstod la ldang bar bya //
T02TD1981E:159b-18: ma he'i sbyor bas rnam par rgyu //
T02TD1981E:159b-19: shin tu rtogs dka'i rgyud las ni //
T02TD1981E:159b-20: las rnams thams cad sbyor ba'i lha //
T02TD1981E:159b-21: zhal gcig phyag gnyis bdag gis bris //
T02TD1981E:159b-22: blo dman rnams la phan phyir ro //
T02TD1981E:159b-23: dge ba cung zad thob pa des //
T02TD1981E:159b-24: bdag dang 'di la mos pa rnams //
T02TD1981E:159b-25: nad dang 'jigs sogs rab bcom nas //
T02TD1981E:159b-26: myur du 'jigs byed chen por shog / slob dpon manydzu shr'i dzny'a nas mdzad pa /
T02TD1981E:159b-27: zhang 'or ston pa shes rab bsod nams kyis bsgyur ba rdzogs so//
